NFO Viewer 1.11
===============

 [X] Fix immediate crash resulting from bad use of Gtk.StyleContext on
     newer versions of PyGObject and/or GTK+ (#687513)
 [X] Remove deprecated 'get_data' and 'set_data' calls
 [X] Use Gtk.Grid for preferences dialog instead of Gtk.Table
 [X] Release source tarballs only compressed as tar.xz (instead
     of the previous tar.gz and tar.bz2)

